{"tid":1683053,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"海洋公園取消明日「哈囉喂全園祭」","createTime":"2019-10-30T12:27:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T12:53:16.000Z","uid":33775,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"cedc5e04f3d3a92f625171c749378499b6445f64","tid":1683053,"uid":33775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T12:27:58.000Z","msg":"海洋公園取消明日「哈囉喂全園祭」<br />\n<br />\n海洋公園表示，決定取消明日「哈囉喂全園祭」項目，對受影響的遊客致歉，持有門票的人士，可於海洋公園網站查詢退票詳情。海洋公園表示，鑑於社會狀況及面對多方不同意見，加上港島多區會有公眾活動，為顧及遊人和員工的安全，經審慎考慮後，決定取消有關項目，公園亦已就決定與相關同事溝通。<br />\n<br />\n2019-10-30 20:20:57<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"237ff38528498ba60c6f459d96993be4d370ec99","tid":1683053,"uid":144849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T12:29:14.000Z","msg":"知啦知啦 第5個啦"},{"pid":"39933b8e45c71060833151821fbe35844e233411","tid":1683053,"uid":147292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T12:32:51.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"a80b210152fd89c7d6211d2d52de5b1ee7df8d59","tid":1683053,"uid":282115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T12:35:28.000Z","msg":"攬炒"},{"pid":"3edd06cd35aff8b95b497bb6c5d5161fa99a85f0","tid":1683053,"uid":76382,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T12:52:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mArr0kk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmArr0kk.jpg&h=5bf9d671&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f6cb5c1607050965930f178acd8ec424b5cff310","tid":1683053,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T12:52:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"971496df66f30bab3c87ab842a459c06b1783937","tid":1683053,"uid":261332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T12:53:16.000Z","msg":"死要面<br />\n人地話罷工你就話放假一天唔洗開工<br />\n<br />\n阿Q 到呢..."}]}